$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
rewrite_field

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
rewrite_field -  This method rewrites local email addresses (as found in mudmail) to be usable outside Discworld, for instance from an email client.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
string rewrite_field(string header_field)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^header_field%^RESET%^ - the string to rewrite
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the new string
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/mime.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method rewrites local email addresses (as found in mudmail)
to be usable outside Discworld, for instance from an email client.
.EP

